	<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading" lang="en">SLiM</h1>
	<div id="bodyContent" class="mw-body-content">
		<div id="siteSub" class="noprint">From ArchWiki</div>
		<div id="contentSub"><span class="mw-redirectedfrom">(Redirected from <a href="/index.php?title=Slim&amp;redirect=no" class="mw-redirect" title="Slim">Slim</a>)</span></div>
		<div id="contentSub2"></div>
		
		<div id="jump-to-nav"></div>
		<a class="mw-jump-link" href="#mw-head">Jump to navigation</a>
		<a class="mw-jump-link" href="#searchInput">Jump to search</a>
		<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="mw-parser-output"><div class="archwiki-template-meta-related-articles-start"><p>Related articles</p><ul>
<li><a href="/index.php/Display_manager" title="Display manager">Display manager</a></li>
</ul></div>
<div class="archwiki-template-box archwiki-template-box-warning"><strong>Warning:</strong> The SliM project has been abandoned (last release was 2013), and is not fully compatible with <a href="/index.php/Systemd" title="Systemd">systemd</a>, including <i>logind</i> sessions. Consider using a different <a href="/index.php/Display_manager" title="Display manager">Display manager</a> or <a href="/index.php/Xinitrc" class="mw-redirect" title="Xinitrc">Xinitrc</a>.</div>
<p><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://sourceforge.net/projects/slim.berlios/">SLiM</a> is an acronym for <b>S</b>imple <b>L</b>og<b>i</b>n <b>M</b>anager. Lightweight and easily configurable, SLiM requires minimal dependencies, and none from  the <a href="/index.php/GNOME" title="GNOME">GNOME</a> or <a href="/index.php/KDE" title="KDE">KDE</a> desktop environments. It therefore contributes towards a lightweight system for users that also like to use lightweight desktops such as <a href="/index.php/Xfce" title="Xfce">Xfce</a>, <a href="/index.php/Openbox" title="Openbox">Openbox</a>, and <a href="/index.php/Fluxbox" title="Fluxbox">Fluxbox</a>.
</p>
<div id="toc" class="toc" role="navigation" aria-labelledby="mw-toc-heading"><input type="checkbox" role="button" id="toctogglecheckbox" class="toctogglecheckbox" style="display:none" /><div class="toctitle" lang="en" dir="ltr"><h2 id="mw-toc-heading">Contents</h2><span class="toctogglespan"><label class="toctogglelabel" for="toctogglecheckbox"></label></span></div>
